'''Mrs. Burnett''' was the wife of [[Clifford Burnett]].

==History==
Mrs. Burnett got married to Clifford Burnett at an unknown time.

In around 1997, she died from a heart attack.

She was mentioned when [[Joey Tribbiani|Joey]] dressed up as a doctor and interrogated her widower for personal information about him to pass on to [[Phoebe Buffay|Phoebe]].
